AmountEndRange.description: The end range of amount for graded percent of premium.

AmountStartRange.description: The start range of amount for graded percent of premium.

CurrencyIsoCode.description: If multiple currencies are enabled, this field contains the currency ISO code associated with the record.

Fee.description: The commission fee when Flat Fee or Capitated Fees are selected.

FeePercent.description: The percentage of fee to be earned as commission when flat percentage of fee is selected.

InsuranceRatePlanId.description: The insurance rate plan associated with the commission.

Name.description: The name of the commission rate plan.

NumberEndRange.description: The end range of the grade volume, which represents the employee count.

NumberStartRange.description: The start range of the grade volume, which represents the employee count.

PremiumPercent.description: The percentage of premium to be earned as commission when graded percent of premium or flat percent of premium is selected.

Type.description: Specifies the type of commission structure.
